description.en: C token is a new conceptive token about environmental protection based on heco smartchain, developed by the international r&d team of the top called Fintech and blockchain enthusiasts. It is a kind of token with the nature of community autonomy. After the completion of the creation airdrop, the project owner destroyed the private key of C token. The community is now completely autonomous, and spontaneously establishes a foundation for ecological construction in the nearly future.
